data.description: This remarkable 2-story  home features an open-concept design that is inviting and comforting, making in the perfect place to call your retreat after a long day! As you step in, you will be greeted by beautiful rich in color hardwoods that just glow. A full formal space that can become whatever you need and a formal dining area and butler's pantry perfect for any gathering or celebration. Whether you are hosting a formal dinner party or a cozy movie night, this home is designed to accommodate your every need.Pull a stool to the breakfast bar and enjoy a casual morning  conversation or a quiet moment, as the sun fills the room with warmth. The kitchen boast a sophistication that you just have to see with your own eyes that flows into the family room.Retreating to your personal oasis, the oversized master suite beckons with its spa-like bath. Imagine unwinding after a long day. The master retreat also boats ample closet space and a separate sitting room that offers so many possibilities.  This home offers generously sized secondary bedrooms that are perfect for family or guests. What are you waiting for? Don't miss the opportunity to make this your forever home.
